    "created_at": "2015-10-20T14:19:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-20T14:19:00Z",
    "body": "I think Chromium team simply never tested the transparency code on machines with DWM disabled, it is an experiment feature and not being actively worked on. So as Chrome's GPU acceleration getting heavily changed, it is very easy to break things.\n"
