    "created_at": "2016-02-02T09:25:24Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-02-02T09:25:24Z",
    "body": "In Chromium window transparency is only enabled for Windows when DWM is enabled, so if we want to ensure window transparency works perfectly we have to disable it on most platforms.\n\nSince now we have API to check whether DWM is enabled, I think it is better to put the choice of whether to enable window transparency to the users.\n"
